divs: Sighting DetailsI took a photo on the way over to a boating party held the 3rd Saturday of August every year. It was mostly a far shot of the boats anchored on the island. When I got home I transfered the photo from my cell phone to my computer and cropped most of the sea and sky away. Thats when I noticed this sky blue object over the island. Just for your information, this island is across the bay from Earle Ammunition base. It was to high in the sky for a balloon which I thought it was at first. I sent the photo on to someone that may have had better close-up program. Here is what I have if I am able to download photos If not then feel free to call or email me HelaineNJ@aol.com or 908-309-9449 Helaine Camacho
Summary: When I took the photo I didnt even see it there. DAYTIME UFO
